CREATE TABLE umbracoUser
(
 "id" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT
, "userDisabled" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoUser_userDisabled" DEFAULT ('0')
, "key" TEXT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoUser_key" DEFAULT (NEWID())
, "userNoConsole" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoUser_userNoConsole" DEFAULT ('0')
, "userName" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NOT NULL
, "userLogin" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NOT NULL
, "userPassword" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NOT NULL
, "passwordConfig" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "userEmail" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NOT NULL
, "userLanguage" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "securityStampToken" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "failedLoginAttempts" INTEGER NULL
, "lastLockoutDate" TEXT NULL
, "lastPasswordChangeDate" TEXT NULL
, "lastLoginDate" TEXT NULL
, "emailConfirmedDate" TEXT NULL
, "invitedDate" TEXT NULL
, "createDate" TEXT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoUser_createDate" DEFAULT (DATE())
, "updateDate" TEXT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoUser_updateDate" DEFAULT (DATE())
, "kind" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoUser_kind" DEFAULT ('0')
, "avatar" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, CONSTRAINT PK_user UNIQUE ("id")
)

CREATE TABLE umbracoNode
(
 "id" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT
, "uniqueId" TEXT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoNode_uniqueId" DEFAULT (NEWID())
, "parentId" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "level" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "path" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NOT NULL
, "sortOrder" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "trashed" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoNode_trashed" DEFAULT ('0')
, "nodeUser" INTEGER NULL
, "text" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "nodeObjectType" TEXT NULL
, "createDate" TEXT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoNode_createDate" DEFAULT (DATE())
, CONSTRAINT PK_umbracoNode UNIQUE ("id")
, CONSTRAINT FK_umbracoNode_umbracoNode_id FOREIGN KEY ("parentId") REFERENCES "umbracoNode" ("id")  
, CONSTRAINT FK_umbracoNode_umbracoUser_id FOREIGN KEY ("nodeUser") REFERENCES "umbracoUser" ("id")  
)

CREATE TABLE cmsContentType
(
 "pk" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT
, "nodeId" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "alias" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "icon" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "thumbnail" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_cmsContentType_thumbnail" DEFAULT ('folder.png')
, "description" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "listView" TEXT NULL
, "isElement" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_cmsContentType_isElement" DEFAULT ('0')
, "allowAtRoot" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_cmsContentType_allowAtRoot" DEFAULT ('0')
, "variations" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_cmsContentType_variations" DEFAULT ('1')
, CONSTRAINT PK_cmsContentType UNIQUE ("pk")
, CONSTRAINT FK_cmsContentType_umbracoNode_id FOREIGN KEY ("nodeId") REFERENCES "umbracoNode" ("id")  
)

CREATE TABLE cmsTemplate
(
 "pk" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT
, "nodeId" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "alias" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, CONSTRAINT PK_cmsTemplate UNIQUE ("pk")
, CONSTRAINT FK_cmsTemplate_umbracoNode FOREIGN KEY ("nodeId") REFERENCES "umbracoNode" ("id")  
)

CREATE TABLE umbracoContent
(
 "nodeId" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "contentTypeId" INTEGER NOT NULL
, CONSTRAINT PK_umbracoContent PRIMARY KEY ("nodeId")
, CONSTRAINT FK_umbracoContent_umbracoNode_id FOREIGN KEY ("nodeId") REFERENCES "umbracoNode" ("id")

)

CREATE TABLE umbracoContentVersion
(
 "id" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT
, "nodeId" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "versionDate" TEXT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoContentVersion_versionDate" DEFAULT (DATE())
, "userId" INTEGER NULL
, "current" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "text" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "preventCleanup" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoContentVersion_preventCleanup" DEFAULT ('0')
, CONSTRAINT PK_umbracoContentVersion UNIQUE ("id")
, CONSTRAINT FK_umbracoContentVersion_umbracoContent_nodeId FOREIGN KEY ("nodeId") REFERENCES "umbracoContent" ("nodeId")  
, CONSTRAINT FK_umbracoContentVersion_umbracoUser_id FOREIGN KEY ("userId") REFERENCES "umbracoUser" ("id")  
)

CREATE TABLE umbracoMediaVersion
(
 "id" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "path" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, CONSTRAINT PK_umbracoMediaVersion PRIMARY KEY ("id")
, CONSTRAINT FK_umbracoMediaVersion_umbracoContentVersion_id FOREIGN KEY ("id") REFERENCES "umbracoContentVersion" ("id")  
)

CREATE TABLE umbracoDocument
(

)

, CONSTRAINT FK_cmsDocumentType_cmsContentType_nodeId FOREIGN KEY ("contentTypeNodeId") REFERENCES "cmsContentType" ("nodeId")  
, CONSTRAINT FK_cmsDocumentType_umbracoNode_id FOREIGN KEY ("contentTypeNodeId") REFERENCES "umbracoNode" ("id")  
, CONSTRAINT FK_cmsDocumentType_cmsTemplate_nodeId FOREIGN KEY ("templateNodeId") REFERENCES "cmsTemplate" ("nodeId")  
)

CREATE TABLE umbracoDataType
(
 "nodeId" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "propertyEditorAlias" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NOT NULL
, "propertyEditorUiAlias" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "dbType" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NOT NULL
, "config" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, CONSTRAINT PK_umbracoDataType PRIMARY KEY ("nodeId")
, CONSTRAINT FK_umbracoDataType_umbracoNode_id FOREIGN KEY ("nodeId") REFERENCES "umbracoNode" ("id")  
)

CREATE TABLE cmsDictionary
(
 "pk" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT
, "id" TEXT NOT NULL
, "parent" TEXT NULL

, CONSTRAINT FK_cmsDictionary_cmsDictionary_id FOREIGN KEY ("parent") REFERENCES "cmsDictionary" ("id")  
)

CREATE TABLE umbracoLanguage
(
 "id" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT
, "languageISOCode" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "languageCultureName" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "isDefaultVariantLang" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoLanguage_isDefaultVariantLang" DEFAULT ('0')
, "mandatory" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoLanguage_mandatory" DEFAULT ('0')
, "fallbackLanguageId" INTEGER NULL
, CONSTRAINT PK_umbracoLanguage UNIQUE ("id")
, CONSTRAINT FK_umbracoLanguage_umbracoLanguage_id FOREIGN KEY ("fallbackLanguageId") REFERENCES "umbracoLanguage" ("id")  
)

CREATE TABLE cmsLanguageText
(
 "pk" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT
, "languageId" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "UniqueId" TEXT NOT NULL
, "value" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NOT NULL
, CONSTRAINT PK_cmsLanguageText UNIQUE ("pk")
, CONSTRAINT FK_cmsLanguageText_umbracoLanguage_id FOREIGN KEY ("languageId") REFERENCES "umbracoLanguage" ("id")  
, CONSTRAINT FK_cmsLanguageText_cmsDictionary_id FOREIGN KEY ("UniqueId") REFERENCES "cmsDictionary" ("id")  
)

CREATE TABLE umbracoDomain
(
 "id" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT
, "domainDefaultLanguage" INTEGER NULL
, "domainRootStructureID" INTEGER NULL
, "domainName" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NOT NULL
, "sortOrder" INTEGER NOT NULL
, CONSTRAINT PK_umbracoDomain UNIQUE ("id")
, CONSTRAINT FK_umbracoDomain_umbracoNode_id FOREIGN KEY ("domainRootStructureID") REFERENCES "umbracoNode" ("id")  
)

CREATE TABLE umbracoLog
(
 "id" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT
, "userId" INTEGER NULL
, "NodeId" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "entityType" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "Datestamp" TEXT NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_umbracoLog_Datestamp" DEFAULT (DATE())
, "logHeader" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NOT NULL
, "logComment" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL
, "parameters" TEXT COLLATE NOCASE NULL

)

CREATE TABLE cmsMemberType
(
 "pk" INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT

, "propertytypeId" INTEGER NOT NULL
, "memberCanEdit" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_cmsMemberType_memberCanEdit" DEFAULT ('0')
, "viewOnProfile" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_cmsMemberType_viewOnProfile" DEFAULT ('0')
, "isSensitive" INTEGER NOT NULL CONSTRAINT "DF_cmsMemberType_isSensitive" DEFAULT ('0')
, CONSTRAINT PK_cmsMemberType UNIQUE ("pk")
, CONSTRAINT FK_cmsMemberType_umbracoNode_id FOREIGN KEY ("NodeId") REFERENCES "umbracoNode" ("id")  
, CONSTRAINT FK_cmsMemberType_cmsContentType_nodeId FOREIGN KEY ("NodeId") REFERENCES "cmsContentType" ("nodeId")  
)

(

, "lastLockoutDate" TEXT NULL
, "lastPasswordChangeDate" TEXT NULL
